{"tid":1454564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錯發颱風致山東全省人死亡 騰訊視頻道歉","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:36:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":593,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"74de4129c28c8c399d4b05dd58a205dfc7fede19","tid":1454564,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"騰訊視頻今午發送了一則山東省應急廳的消息，指<span style=\"color: red;\">「颱風利奇馬已致全省人死亡，7人失蹤」</span>。隨後，騰訊視頻官方微博就事件道歉。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊視頻指，在剛推送的一則關於山東汛情的消息中，因編輯失誤造成文案中遇難人數的缺失，發現後立即進行了更正。<br />\n<br />\n對於產生的不良影響，騰訊視頻致以誠摯的歉意，並指今後發布新聞會嚴加審核，杜絕此類錯誤再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊視頻隨後訂正遇難人數為5人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2217528/%E9%8C%AF%E7%99%BC%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E8%87%B4%E5%B1%B1%E6%9D%B1%E5%85%A8%E7%9C%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1+%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2217528%2F%25E9%258C%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259C%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2B%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=23d85985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2217528/%E9%8C%AF%E7%99%BC%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E8%87%B4%E5%B1%B1%E6%9D%B1%E5%85%A8%E7%9C%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1+%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"efd1db4f25345e94c68f6330e6fd504070552621","tid":1454564,"uid":271250,"like":514,"dislike":1,"score":513,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"一時口快報左真相"},{"pid":"89f4ad066221b3b8116a43deb07a3b2b051e4ffb","tid":1454564,"uid":298077,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"真新聞要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj